dcterms:description: SWAN-SF is a benchmark dataset consisting of multivariate time series data for solar flare prediction. It contains 4,075 data instances from active regions of 10,000 flare reports over 8 years, with each instance representing a 12-hour observation window of 51 flare-predictive parameters.
dcterms:title: SWAN-SF
